    "requirement": "Implement a return-eligibility feature that evaluates a return request for a single purchased line item (purchase date, item type, price, and whether it was marked as clearance). The feature must use an abstract base class for return policies and at least two derived policy classes that override eligibility logic. Use a policy factory/selector to choose the correct policy at runtime and demonstrate the difference between static and instance members by keeping a static catalog of policy selectors while using instance policy objects to evaluate requests."
