    "requirement": "Implement a feature that exports a todo list (title + items) into a formatted string based on a requested export format. The exporter must retrieve the list and items through a repository abstraction. The exporter must select the export algorithm at runtime using a strategy abstraction and obtain the strategy via a factory. The feature must be testable without I/O by returning the export content as a string."
