    "Start with the repository returning a simple in-memory list object so you can focus on patterns rather than persistence.",
    "If you’re about to write 'if format == \"csv\"' in the exporter, move that decision to a factory.",
    "Make your formatter output deterministic by ordering items (e.g., by id) before formatting.",
