    "requirement": "Implement a standalone shipping-cost feature that calculates shipping for a basket using rule objects. Model shipping rules using inheritance with an abstract base class and derived rule types that override matching and pricing behavior. Use composition for the basket holding items with weight. Use LINQ to select the best applicable rule from a list. Return a result object with the chosen service name, base cost, any surcharge, and final shipping cost."
