    "Implement subtotal first by looping over items and summing unitPrice * quantity; add validation checks for quantity and price while you loop.",
    "Next, implement tiered discounts with if/else if/else using clear subtotal thresholds (e.g., small/medium/large orders).",
    "Add promo code handling as an extra discount that depends on more than one condition (e.g., promo code AND minimum subtotal).",
    "Finally, implement payment fee selection with a switch statement so each payment method has its own rule."
