    "Convert the weight header into a numeric type (double is acceptable). Convert the expedited header into a boolean. If conversion fails, treat the request as invalid.",
    "Validate the inputs using boolean expressions: weight must be greater than 0, zone must be one of the supported values, and expedited must be provided. If invalid, set status code 400, write a short error message to the response body, and do not call the next delegate.",
