    "requirement": "Implement ONE feature: correlation id propagation for API requests. Add an action filter that ensures every request has a correlation id (from a request header or generated). The filter must store it in HttpContext.Items, log it, and ensure the controller response includes it. Also, extend centralized exception handling so ProblemDetails/ValidationProblemDetails responses include the same correlation id field. Register the filter and any needed services in Program.cs."
