    "requirement": "Implement a single feature: a small EF Core-backed store credit ledger module. Model credits and their applications, configure them in a DbContext, and implement a query method that returns customers with remaining credit (after applications), sorted by most urgent-to-use credit (earliest expiry) and including a projected summary (no full entity graph returned)."
